moodle_exam.title: End Semester Examination
moodle_exam.description:
Read the instruction carefully:

1. This is a proctored online examination, where you are monitored every minute under camera, keeps an eye over your activities regularly without break. 

2. Keep your examination desk under adequate light without any Reading and Writing material around the desk except for your system (Laptop/Desktop).

3. Keep your Laptop/Desktop camera ON 10 minutes before the scheduled examination time.

4.  Frequent movement of heads along axial line, toward right/left of your sitting position and tilted sitting position, will be identified by proctored software. So, please maintain upright sitting posture throughout the exam to avoid camera declaring you using unfair means. 

5. All the Best for your Examination.

moodle_quiz.title: Quiz - II
moodle_quiz.description:
Instructions for Quiz-II

Availability: The quiz will be open from
5-November-2025 (12:00 AM) to 11-November-2025 (11:59 PM).

Number of attempts: Only 1 attempt is allowed.

Duration: The quiz must be completed within 1 hour from the time you start.

Example: If you start at 2:30 PM, the quiz will automatically close at 3:30 PM, even if you have not submitted.

Login Requirement: You must use your Institute Moodle login to access the quiz.

Important:

  • Do not refresh, close the browser, or open new tabs once the quiz has started.

  • Ensure you have a stable internet connection before beginning.

  • Any form of malpractice will result in disqualification and disciplinary action.
